TVH Position:
- Receives: SecuritySurfaceModel from Security Semantics Stratum
- Produces: ThreatVectorSet (ranked, scored attack vectors)
- Integrated with: AHS (for risk-weighted prioritization)
- Feeds into: Narrative (human-readable threat brief)Isi:

1. Purpose

TVH (Threat Vector Hypothesis) adalah subsistem yang mengubah SecuritySurfaceModel menjadi ranked catalog of potential attack vectors berbasis arsitektur.
TVH ≠ Vulnerability Scanner

TVH tidak:

    ❌ Mendeteksi CVE spesifik
    ❌ Menghasilkan exploit payload
    ❌ Melakukan vulnerability confirmation

TVH hanya:

    ✅ Mengidentifikasi structural weaknesses berbasis arsitektur
    ✅ Me-rank vector berbasis likelihood × impact × feasibility
    ✅ Memetakan vector ke manual testing procedures

Philosophy:

Architecture → Attack Surface → Threat Vector → Testing Strategy

TVH adalah bridge antara "what we know about the system" dan "what pentester should test".
